  "title": "Mateo Curved Rattan Dining Chair - Set of Two - Walnut",
  "description": "\u003cp\u003eUpgrade your dining space with the Mateo Curved Rattan Dining Chair set. Featuring a sturdy rubber wood frame, honeycomb rattan back, and cushioned woven seat, these chairs blend comfort with a modern cottage style. Perfect for a cosy kitchen or stylish dining area, the curved design adds a timeless, on-trend touch to your home. Easy to assemble.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStylish Comfort\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe curved rattan back and cushioned seat combine beauty and comfort. Designed in a modern cottage style, these chairs are perfect for creating welcoming dining spaces.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDurable Design\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eMade from solid rubber wood and woven rattan, these chairs offer strength and long-lasting value. The sturdy frame ensures reliable seating for every meal and gathering.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEasy Assembly\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eWith straightforward assembly instructions, setting up your Mateo Dining Chairs is simple. Enjoy fuss-free construction and quick results, making it easy to refresh your dining area.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSolid rubber wood frame\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHoneycomb rattan back\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCushioned woven rattan seat\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eModern cottage style\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDesigned in-house\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThis product is not suitable for commercial use.",
