  "handle": "amara-six-seater-dining-table-walnut",
  "title": "Amara Six Seater Dining Table - Walnut",
  "description": "\u003cp\u003eMake every meal a moment to enjoy with the Amara Six Seater Dining Table - Walnut. This stylish oval-shaped table is perfect for family dinners or entertaining friends. Crafted from durable MDF with a melamine finish, its timeless mid-century design suits both modern and classic dining spaces. The curved, fluted legs add subtle elegance to your home.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSeating for Six\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe Amara dining table comfortably fits six people, making it ideal for family dinners or hosting gatherings. Its oval shape promotes easy seating and fosters connection around the table.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDurable Design\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eDesigned with a solid MDF base and a wood-look melamine top finish, the table is easy to maintain and resistant to daily wear.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStylish Features\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe curved legs with fluted detailing bring a touch of mid-century charm, enhancing the look of your dining area without overwhelming your existing furniture or decor.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e  \u003cli\u003eSeats up to six people\u003c\/li\u003e  \u003cli\u003eDurable melamine top finish\u003c\/li\u003e  \u003cli\u003eMid-century inspired oval shape\u003c\/li\u003e  \u003cli\u003eElegant curved, fluted legs\u003c\/li\u003e  \u003cli\u003eDesigned in-house\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThis product is not suitable for commercial use.",
