  "id": 10308059955475,
  "available": true,
  "vendor": "Mocka Australia",
  "handle": "mateo-curved-rattan-bar-stool-walnut",
  "title": "Mateo Curved Rattan Bar Stool - Walnut",
  "description": "\u003cp\u003eAdd a touch of coastal style to your home with the Mateo Curved Rattan Bar Stool in Walnut. Crafted with durable rubber wood and natural rattan, it features a honeycomb rattan back and cushioned woven seat for comfort. Perfect for kitchen counters or bar spaces, its deep walnut tones and timeless design suit both modern and classic interiors.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eComfortable Design\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe curved backrest and cushioned woven seat offer comfortable support during meals or gatherings, making it ideal for everyday use in kitchens, dining spaces, or casual bar settings.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eQuality Materials\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eMade with strong rubber wood and natural rattan, this stool is built to last. The honeycomb rattan back adds style and airflow for comfort in warmer weather.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCoastal Style\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eIts deep walnut finish pairs beautifully with the natural rattan detail, creating a relaxed, coastal feel. Perfect for homes wanting a timeless yet modern touch for their bar or counter space.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDurable rubber wood frame\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHoneycomb rattan backrest\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCushioned woven rattan seat\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCoastal walnut and natural tones\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDesigned in-house\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThis product is not suitable for commercial use.",
