  "id": 9762290139411,
  "available": true,
  "vendor": "Mocka Australia",
  "handle": "amara-bench-seat-natural",
  "title": "Amara Bench Seat - Natural",
  "description": "\u003cp\u003eElevate your dining area with the Amara Bench Seat. Perfect for two, this seat pairs well with the Amara Dining Table. Its curved seat and stylish base make it a modern pick for any home. Made for lasting use, it's easy to care for and looks great.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eBuilt to Last\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe Amara Bench is super sturdy. Made with tough MDF and a solid melamine finish, it's ready for whatever daily life throws at it, all without a fuss.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eLooks Great\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThis bench brings a modern flair to any space. With its cool curved seat and neat base, it’s a hit for anyone wanting to spice up their home’s style.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eComfy Sitting\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt’s the perfect spot for two to sit back and relax. Whether you’re eating, chatting, or just chilling, the Amara Bench’s curve makes it extra comfy for everyone.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDurable MDF construction\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eModern curved seat\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStylish fluted base\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDesigned in-house\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThis product is not suitable for commercial use.",
