  "handle": "amara-bench-seat-walnut",
  "title": "Amara Bench Seat - Walnut",
  "description": "\u003cp\u003eThe Amara Bench Seat - Walnut is a stylish two-seater bench, perfect for any dining or living space. Crafted from durable MDF with a melamine finish, it features a curved seat and fluted legs in a stunning dark walnut tone. Inspired by mid-century design, this versatile piece suits both modern and classic interiors.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDurable Design\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eMade from solid MDF with a melamine top, the Amara Bench Seat is built to last. Its tough surface resists scratches and spills, making it perfect for everyday use.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMid-Century Style\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe dark walnut colour and curved design bring a touch of mid-century charm to your home. The stylish fluted legs add elegance to any dining or living area.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVersatile Seating\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eWhether at the dining table or in the hallway, this two-seater bench fits any room. It offers comfortable seating and a sleek, space-saving alternative to traditional chairs.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDurable MDF with melamine finish\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStylish dark walnut colour\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCurved seat and fluted legs\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eComfortable two-seater design\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDesigned in-house\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThis product is not suitable for commercial use.",
