  "vendor": "Mocka Australia",
  "handle": "amara-six-seater-dining-table-natural",
  "title": "Amara Six Seater Dining Table - Natural",
  "description": "\u003cp\u003eBring timeless coastal style to your dining room with the Amara Six Seater Dining Table. Featuring a curved top and fluted legs, its warm wood-look finish complements any décor. Made from durable MDF with a melamine coating, it’s perfect for everyday family meals or casual entertaining.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStylish Design\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe curved top and fluted legs bring a modern coastal look to any dining space. Its timeless style fits seamlessly with both classic and contemporary décor.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEasy Maintenance\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eMade from MDF with a durable melamine finish, this table resists scratches and spills. Simply wipe clean, making it perfect for busy households and everyday use.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVersatile Fit\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe warm wood-look finish matches any colour scheme, enhancing your space without clashing. Seats six comfortably, ideal for family meals or casual gatherings with friends.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eModern coastal design\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCurved top, fluted legs\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWarm wood-look finish\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDesigned in-house\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThis product is not suitable for commercial use.",
