  "handle": "coco-boucle-dining-chair-cream-walnut",
  "title": "Coco Boucle Dining Chair - Set of 2 - Cream\/Walnut",
  "description": "\u003cp\u003eUpgrade your dining space with the Coco Boucle Dining Chair - Set of 2. Featuring a premium cushioned seat and back for comfort, solid rubberwood legs for durability, and a warm walnut finish, these chairs are inspired by timeless mid-century design. The textured cream fabric suits modern, cosy dining rooms, bringing style and practicality to everyday meals.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eComfortable Seating\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe Coco Boucle Dining Chairs feature a premium upholstered cushioned seat and back, providing excellent support and comfort for long dinners or gatherings with family and friends.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDurable Design\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eCrafted with solid rubberwood legs, these chairs are strong and durable. They are built to withstand daily use and provide long-lasting quality for your dining area.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStylish Appeal\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eInspired by mid-century design, the warm walnut finish and textured cream fabric add a touch of elegance. Suitable for modern or cosy dining rooms, these chairs seamlessly blend style and function.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e  \u003cli\u003ePremium cushioned seat and back\u003c\/li\u003e  \u003cli\u003eSolid rubberwood legs\u003c\/li\u003e  \u003cli\u003eMid-century style inspiration\u003c\/li\u003e  \u003cli\u003eWarm walnut finish\u003c\/li\u003e  \u003cli\u003eDesigned in-house\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThis product is not suitable for commercial use.",
