  "handle": "mateo-curved-rattan-bar-stool-natural",
  "title": "Mateo Curved Rattan Bar Stool - Natural",
  "description": "\u003cp\u003eIntroducing the Mateo Curved Rattan Bar Stool - Natural by Mocka! The style boasts a solid rubber wood frame, is easy to put together, and has a comfortable rattan seat with a fashionably curved back. Great for adding that modern coastal charm to your kitchen, dining area, or home bar that you have always wanted.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSturdy Frame\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe Mateo bar stool has a solid rubber wood frame. That makes it strong and durable, ideal for daily use in your kitchen or dining room.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEasy Assembly\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eWith easy instructions and simple assembly, you can have your new bar stool set up in no time. No special tools or professional help needed.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCoastal Style\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eIts natural rattan seat and curved back give it a modern coastal look. It’s a great way to bring a beachy feel to your home.\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSolid rubber wood frame\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eComfy rattan seat\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEasy to assemble\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStylish curved back\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDesigned in-house\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThis product is not suitable for commercial use.",
